{"id": "ChIJYbQ9hF3HwoAR-rB5iRVgpMs", "rating": 4.9, "userRatingCount": 8, "displayName": {"text": "Woody", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJYbQ9hF3HwoAR-rB5iRVgpMs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxcFZEVk1PV3RXVkRGTWVUQnpXR3QyWlhwdmVrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Picked up several of their textured rib tee- the fit was great, very comfortable tees, a good friend introduced them to me and we’ll be back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Picked up several of their textured rib tee- the fit was great, very comfortable tees, a good friend introduced them to me and we’ll be back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chris Lyons", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115085052836999838341/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsZs5R8P-UrRTvU3pUCpoXM1J9hhiIA-lijjFIb-We5uDc_76hQw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-03T00:17:46.593011760Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxcFZEVk1PV3RXVkRGTWVUQnpXR3QyWlhwdmVrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxcFZEVk1PV3RXVkRGTWVUQnpXR3QyWlhwdmVrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c75d843db461:0xcba460158979b0fa"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYbQ9hF3HwoAR-rB5iRVgpMs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kwdFoybEJNM1puTjJWMU1rNHlNMVZ2VEhGV09IYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Love it !! ", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Love it !! ", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "문채영", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100726282020490259040/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_TSsWg52DvAOnhOSmAP0TWWZ55n3zhGw0jvcjyH6inNTZFK_k=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-28T20:14:12.407532503Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kwdFoybEJNM1puTjJWMU1rNHlNMVZ2VEhGV09IYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kwdFoybEJNM1puTjJWMU1rNHlNMVZ2VEhGV09IYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c75d843db461:0xcba460158979b0fa"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYbQ9hF3HwoAR-rB5iRVgpMs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSbFgwUk9kVjl3U1Rob1MzVm9hVk5CTjFaVmVtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a week ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Very honest and quality products and service. Just got a NOMANUAL brand jacket based in Korea for $130 at this store, first item I bought despite going here a few times with friends already. I wouldn't mind paying an extra $20-30 for imports fee but wow, they did not even adjust the price, and sold it for $130 retail????? Wow. I have to say the only thing that dissapointed me is that pants here are not ideal for whoever is 5'4 (162.5cm) and under, and I blame myself for that.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very honest and quality products and service. Just got a NOMANUAL brand jacket based in Korea for $130 at this store, first item I bought despite going here a few times with friends already. I wouldn't mind paying an extra $20-30 for imports fee but wow, they did not even adjust the price, and sold it for $130 retail????? Wow. I have to say the only thing that dissapointed me is that pants here are not ideal for whoever is 5'4 (162.5cm) and under, and I blame myself for that.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Bob Thebuilder", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117126275621197417506/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJL8VF2QTOjre54Z19zVmraQVekEvnCKXONjkIvMcBCVixJUg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-30T19:20:20.586588312Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSbFgwUk9kVjl3U1Rob1MzVm9hVk5CTjFaVmVtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSbFgwUk9kVjl3U1Rob1MzVm9hVk5CTjFaVmVtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c75d843db461:0xcba460158979b0fa"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYbQ9hF3HwoAR-rB5iRVgpMs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toSk0zQm5OMVZYZDFsMVExY3RVM0pUT0U1TE1rRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "cool clothing store with pieces and accessories sourced from korea! the decor is very similar to the trendy indie shops you would find in asia nowadays. their music also matches the vibes of the store. most pieces are fairly priced and not outrageously expensive. I got a pair of well-made oversized bermuda shorts (with hella pockets) for $80!\n\nthere are also three spacious changing rooms at the back of the store, and staff is helpful and friendly.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "cool clothing store with pieces and accessories sourced from korea! the decor is very similar to the trendy indie shops you would find in asia nowadays. their music also matches the vibes of the store. most pieces are fairly priced and not outrageously expensive. I got a pair of well-made oversized bermuda shorts (with hella pockets) for $80!\n\nthere are also three spacious changing rooms at the back of the store, and staff is helpful and friendly.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sophie Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115921679004469073625/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2luqsywa0_YWsAZ0okKdmzPDAp7EZrzCbmfqfY9ua0VycayFEVA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-20T18:44:53.632258466Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toSk0zQm5OMVZYZDFsMVExY3RVM0pUT0U1TE1rRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m